  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK690">
<l>iṟuti payappiṉu meñcā tiṟaivaṟ </l>
<l>kuṟuti payappatān tūtu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the ambassador who fearlessly seeks his sovereign's good though it should cost him his life (to deliver his message).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
